        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教學】AI 幫你自製 WhatsApp Sticker，由想 Idea 至生成圖片、匯入 WhatsApp 教學</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/ai-make-sticker-for-whatsapp/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 12:02:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303155</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ChatGPT 早前升級了 GPT-4o 圖片生成功能，推出「創作圖像」功能，讓用家可以生成各種不同風格如漫畫、吉卜力風格等的圖片。現時我們也可以透過其「創作圖像」功能，輕鬆製作有自己、親友樣子的貼圖。以下小編將會和大家分享如何使用 ChatGPT 幫你自動生成 WhatsApp 貼圖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303243" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk14.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可生成各種風格的個人 sticker</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0429.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可在 WhatsApp 上使用</p><h2>需求</h2><p>ChatGPT 帳户（免費每日僅可生成 3 張，因此建議訂閲 Pro 或 Plus ）</p><p>VPN（香港用户需要 VPN 方可使用到 ChatGPT，台灣則不需要）</p><p>WhatsApp（貼圖也可匯出到 LINE 拍貼應用程式）</p><h2>Step 1 使用 ChatGPT「創作圖像」</h2><p>開啟 VPN 後，登入 ChatGPT 帳户，開啟一個新對話，選擇「創作圖像」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk1.jpg 968w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「創作圖像」</p><br /><b>
根據圖片人物衣著、外貌特徵，生成 3 張美少女戰士式風格方形貼圖，人物表情需要為開懷大笑、憤怒和肚餓。</p><p>輸入好指令之後就可以點擊發送，稍後片刻待 ChatGPT 幫你生成貼圖。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303200" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445755.jpg 885w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> ▲上傳圖片並輸入指令</p><p>不消一陣 ChatGPT 就可幫你生成 3 張方形的圖片。你可以要求 ChatGPT 幫你再修改貼圖，小編想 ChatGPT 重新繪畫肚餓，因為貼圖看起來與憤怒無異。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809-559x580.jpg" alt="" width="559" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809-559x580.jpg 559w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445809.jpg 867w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 559px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904-507x580.jpg" alt="" width="507" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904-507x580.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041445904.jpg 786w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 507px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲生成了 3 張圖片，但憤怒和肚餓看起來都一樣</p><p>小編輸入指令「肚餓看起來與憤怒差不多，請更改肚餓圖，使主角看起來肚餓而不是憤怒。」稍等一陣 ChatGPT 就可更新貼圖。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231-563x580.jpg" alt="" width="563" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231-563x580.jpg 563w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041450231.jpg 713w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 563px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲已更新貼圖</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Step 3 加上文字</h2><p>現在你可以輸入指令：「在 3 張貼圖上面加上文字效果」，不過由於小編曾要求 ChatGPT 更改肚餓版本貼圖，因此就加入了一句「請使用最新版本的肚餓」。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129-477x580.jpg" alt="" width="477" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129-477x580.jpg 477w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041451129.jpg 740w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 477px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加入了文字的 Sticker</p><h2>Step 4 加入更多細節</h2><p>你可以要求 ChatGPT 幫你潤飾貼圖，例如加入更多細節。首先點擊圖片，在綠色欄輸入你的要求。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4-628x580.jpg" alt="" width="628" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4-628x580.jpg 628w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk4.jpg 975w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 628px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在綠色欄輸入你的要求</p><p>小編使用指令如下：請加入一個思想氣泡，氣泡內有一碗飯</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455055.jpg 801w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在綠色欄輸入你的要求</p><p>不消一陣 ChatGPT 就按照我要求加入了一碗飯。你可以要求 ChatGPT 加入更多細節，你的貼圖就會更精緻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301-588x580.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301-588x580.jpg 588w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041455301.jpg 813w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 588px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新增了一碗飯</p><p>下面是小編要求 ChatGPT 加入更多細節的圖片，指令可參考圖片下方説明：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-7-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲請加入一個思想氣泡，氣泡內有一碗飯</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-8-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在背景加入大量卡通柴犬、可愛小貓小狗，顯示主角真的很開心</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-9-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在背景加入蘑菇雲爆炸效果，顯示圖中主角真的很憤怒</p><h2>Step 5 下載圖片</h2><p>現在就可以下載你的貼圖。移動滑鼠至圖片上即可見到「下載」按鍵。點擊即可下載</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/stk3.jpg 888w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊即可下載</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-12-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>不過要留意，偶爾 ChatGPT 生成的中文會怪怪的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/chatgptimage20254140-11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「肚餓到暈」的「餓」和「暈」有點怪</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
